# RM Mangoes — environment variables
#
# Copy this file to `.env.local` and fill in values as you enable features.
# The site runs fully without any of these set.

# --- Contact form email delivery (optional) -------------------------------
# The /api/contact route is ready for an email provider. To enable delivery,
# add a provider (e.g. Resend) and set the values below, then wire them up in
# src/app/api/contact/route.ts (see the TODO block there).

# RESEND_API_KEY=
# ORDER_INBOX=info@rmmangoes.co.uk
